description:
Loki season 1 wrapped up on a massive cliffhanger, with Sylvie kick starting the Multiverse and Kang conquering the TVA. And we may not have to wait long to see what's next. Tom Hiddleston is reported to return as Loki in Doctor Strange: The multiverse of Madness--along with the Scarlet Witch, Baron Mordo, and Spider-Man.

We break down what could happen next and how this lays the groundwork for what's happening next in the MCU.
